1
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,040
Meddlesome.

2
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,440
A man.

3
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:40,840
You two

4
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:43,520
are quite skilled.

5
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:45,600
What brings you

6
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:47,640
to Er City?

7
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,040
None of your business.

8
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,400
In Er City,

9
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:53,040
every brick, tile, person, and object

10
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:55,800
is related to my master.

11
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,880
Since you're here.

12
00:03:58,079 --> 00:04:00,000
Then don't be in a rush to leave.

13
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:04,600
Either stay as guests of Ercheng

14
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,640
and serve my master,

15
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:09,640
or in another way,

16
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:12,640
stay here forever.

17
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,440
So many monsters.

18
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,960
So according to you,

19
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:28,440
Ercheng doesn't belong to the government,

20
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:30,160
but to your master?

21
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:33,480
The government? Hahaha.

22
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,760
Those two old dogs in the government,

23
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:39,600
if it weren't for our master's generosity,

24
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:43,159
we would have eaten them long ago.

25
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:45,840
Say no more, everyone.

26
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:46,770
What will you do?

27
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:48,680
Make your choice.

28
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:51,600
This Taoist priest's idea...

29
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:53,880
Naturally, I wouldn't dare to make wild guesses.

30
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:57,240
But I'd like to propose another option.

31
00:04:57,680 --> 00:05:02,280
Why not have your master give this outer city to me?

32
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:04,200
Serve me well,

33
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,960
and I will surely lead you

34
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:07,880
to a brighter future.

35
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:09,440
How about it?

36
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,650
Have mercy, Daoist Master!

37
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:29,160
Save me!

38
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:30,080
No matter.

39
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,560
You can handle it.

40
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:48,680
Divine Taiji.

41
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:49,970
Qiankun Alignment.

42
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:51,280
Nanming Lihuo.

43
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:53,370
Boundless Blazing Flames.

44
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:56,440
Li Position,

45
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,720
activate!

46
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:44,159
Thank you so much for just now.

47
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,320
It was nothing.

48
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:46,640
Don't mention it.

49
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:48,880
Sister Gesang,

50
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:49,960
you hurt your hand.

51
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:51,520
It's just a scratch.

52
00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:53,280
It's bleeding a lot. Let me bandage it for you.

53
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:54,480
Don't touch my blood.

54
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:03,680
Thanks. I'll handle it myself.

55
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,610
Put your clothes on.

56
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:08,760
How do I wear this?

57
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:15,720
Never mind.

58
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,520
First thing tomorrow morning,

59
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:19,120
go buy yourself a new outfit.

60
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:20,520
Okay.

61
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:23,080
And you.

62
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:24,840
Didn't I tell you

63
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,520
not to follow me anymore?

64
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:30,480
Master Daoist, it's not appropriate to say that now.

65
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,800
If I weren't here,

66
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:34,559
you would have been fighting five against one.

67
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:37,760
They are not the mortals from the wilderness inn.

68
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:38,559
Sister,

69
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:40,159
you're wrong about that.

70
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,360
Even if the Master fought five against one,

71
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,360
he wouldn't lose.

72
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:46,040
He can turn into an immortal. A great immortal!

73
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:52,600
Master,

74
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:54,600
you heard it just now.

75
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:58,000
The demons in Ercheng are more than just these.

76
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,400
I am Gesang.

77
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:03,840
Seeing that you are quite interested in this,

78
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:04,970
why don't we team up?

79
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:07,480
We can investigate it together.

80
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:09,080
I am used to acting alone.

81
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,560
No need to trouble yourself.

82
00:09:10,560 --> 00:09:14,000
We have things to do at the government office tomorrow morning.

83
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:14,600
Farewell.

84
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:17,000
Master! Master!

85
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,400
Where are you going?

86
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,200
Back to my room.

87
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,080
We are still staying here?

88
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:20,640
Or else,

89
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:22,690
you can find another place.

90
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:24,200
No, no.

91
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,600
I am safer following you.

92
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:28,600
Master,

93
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:30,410
teach me that move you just did.

94
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:32,200
Shut up.

95
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:58,000
I still underestimated you.

96
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,080
Wake up.

97
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,120
Master.

98
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:03,090
Wake up, Master.

99
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,050
Master, this...

100
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:06,800
Go away.

101
00:10:16,760 --> 00:10:17,920
You didn't sleep all night.

102
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:19,000
How could I dare to sleep?

103
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,680
What if more monsters come?

104
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:22,880
I've already set up a barrier around us.

105
00:10:23,160 --> 00:10:24,960
Monsters won't get in so easily.

106
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:27,520
You should have told me earlier.

107
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:31,000
Master, it's already dawn.

108
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,400
Let's hurry to the yamen.

109
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:34,800
I've never seen you this active before.

110
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,120
Once we hand over the goods,

111
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:38,080
we can get out of this dump.

112
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,320
Not 'we'.

113
00:10:40,280 --> 00:10:41,680
After the goods are handed over,

114
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:42,640
you go your way,

115
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:43,920
and I go mine.

116
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:47,520
From then on, your business has nothing to do with me.

117
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:07,010
Morning.

118
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:08,720
Have some breakfast.

119
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:10,040
Ercheng is so weird.

120
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:11,400
It's so lively at night,

121
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:14,800
but there isn't even a single breakfast stall in the morning.

122
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:17,720
I brought this myself. Try some.

123
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:23,760
Try it.

124
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:28,680
You are so sweet.

125
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:30,680
Eat more.

126
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:17,860
Since ancient times, official lands have been protected by gods.

127
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:20,320
Now the immortal magic here is very weak.

128
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:22,600
The magical objects are broken,

129
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:24,120
and their power is gone.

130
00:12:27,280 --> 00:12:28,080
It seems

131
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:31,120
what the cat demon said last night was true.

132
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:34,720
Kid.

133
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,880
Report to the officials!

134
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:48,720
Report to the officials!

135
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:55,720
What's the matter?

136
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:57,120
Hey, I, I, I...

137
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,200
What are you doing?

138
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,560
Report to the officials!

139
00:12:59,560 --> 00:13:01,090
Report to the authorities.

140
00:14:07,160 --> 00:14:07,480
Muqiang Haihui.

141
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:07,840
Pingjie Qianghai.
